title: Open Bar #85 - Dune 2 Discussion, Madame Web Blame Game, Brie Larson Done With MCU?
description:
As Dune 2 scores a win with critics, Madame Web falls off a cliff and everyone looks for someone to blame i.e the fans. Meanwhile, is Brie Larson looking to exit the MCU? Join me, MauLer, Nerdrotic, Robert Meyer Burnett and Little Platoon as we find out.
